FBIS3-37236 "drsov031_i_94005" FBIS-SOV-94-031 Document Type:Daily Report 15 Feb 1994 CENTRAL ASIA Kazakhstan U.S. Embassy Rejects Accusation Against Official LD1202114894 Almaty Kazakh Radio Network in Russian 0500 GMT 12 Feb 94 LD1202114894 Almaty Kazakh Radio Network Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Text] The U.S. Embassy in Kazakhstan has issued a statement. It announces that no U.S. Government official is in any way involved in the dispute between the mayor of Almaty and a Kazakhstan business leader. Articles that have recently appeared in the local press which contained detailed implications do not have any foundation. Apart from that, it says in the statement, there is no such U.S. official by the name of (Dime Piece).
